  "purpose": "A signed agreement between the organization and a customer, partner, vendor, or grantor that has its own lifecycle: drafted, in review, signed, active, renewable, expiring, terminated. Distinct from Quote (a pre-signature pricing proposal) and from Document (a generic file attachment) — Contract carries terms, dates, parties, and signature metadata as structured data.",
